    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1931-01-21T22:45:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1931-01-21T22:45:00-05:00" n="748"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d748">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">812.48/3831: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The President of Mexico</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ortiz Rubio</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to President <persName type="to"
                            >Hoover</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Mexico</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-01-21T20:45:00-07:00"
                            >January 21, 1931—8:45 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received January 22—12:29 a.m.]<note n="1" xml:id="d748fn1">Received
                            in the Department of State on January 26.</note>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>On behalf of the people of my country I deeply thank you for the sympathy which
                    you were pleased to extend to the Mexican Nation in <pb facs="0822" n="702"
                        xml:id="pg_702"/> the name of the noble American Nation. On my own part I
                    also thank the people of the United States for their expression of sympathy as
                    well as you for the personal sentiments you express as their worthy Chief
                    Magistrate.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">P. Ortiz Rubio</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
